{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"9ec583485b","title":"为日军进攻华北致来哲元等电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"663d2c6df3","index":0,"year":1937,"month":7,"day":8,"articleId":"9ec583485b"}],"tags":[{"id":"0ed2104fe1","name":"徐向前","type":"人物"},{"id":"ae0a6697a5","name":"彭德怀","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"d0a2337495","name":"贺龙","type":"人物"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji10","name":"毛泽东全集第10卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji10.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji10":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"d47d89c5db","type":"paragraph","text":"为日军进攻华北致来哲元等电口","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji10","articleId":"9ec583485b"},{"id":"afd6d628ef","type":"paragraph","text":"（1937年7月8日）北平宋明轩先生、天津张自忠先生、张家口刘汝明先生、保定冯治安先生勋鉴：日定进攻，全国震惯，卢沟桥之役，二十九军英勇抵抗，全国闻风，愿为后盾。敢艺策励全军，为保卫平津而战，为保卫华北面战，不让日宠侵占祖国寸土，为保卫国士，流最后一滴血！红军将士，义债填胸，准备陆时调动，追随贵军与日宽决一死战。除电将委员长，及全国友军请缓杀敌外，特此奉达，即析明教","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji10","articleId":"9ec583485b"},{"id":"741878c564","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东朱德彭德怀贺龙林彪刘伯承徐向前吧","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji10","articleId":"9ec583485b"},{"id":"e5e4a11a62","type":"paragraph","text":"庚玄徐向前吧[1]这是毛泽东和朱、彭德怀、贺龙、林虑、刘伯承、徐向简等7位红军将领为日您进攻华北致北平求明轩、天津张自忠、张家口刘妆明、保定","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji10","articleId":"9ec583485b"}],"page":{"id":"a090179bc3","publicationId":"maoquanji10","articleId":"9ec583485b","start":404,"end":404}}}},"__N_SSG":true}